## Practical: Building a TikTok Clone using Next.js

# Objective

The main objective of this practical was to build a simple TikTok-like web application using Next.js. Through this task, I wanted to understand how a modern web application is structured and how different pages can be connected in a single project. This practical also helped me understand how reusable components can make development easier.



# Technologies Used

In this project, I used several technologies to build the application:

* Next.js
* React.js
* JavaScript
* CSS
* Node.js

Next.js and React were mainly used to create the pages and components, while CSS was used to design the layout of the application.



# Project Structure

The project is organised using folders so that the files are easier to manage. The main part of the project is inside the **src** folder where the application pages and components are stored.

